# 安全缺陷优先级矩阵 (影响 × 修复成本)
# 源: security-concerns.md §优先级矩阵

direction: right

title: "安全缺陷优先级（影响 vs 修复成本）" { near: top-center; shape: text; style.font-size: 20 }

Q_LOW_COST_HIGH_IMPACT: "左上 · 立刻封堵 (成本低, 影响大)" {
  SEC001: "SEC-001 ACL 不对称"
  SEC007: "SEC-007 WSS SSRF"
  SEC008: "SEC-008 启动 fail-open"
  SEC002: "SEC-002 to_http_base 降级"
  SEC010: "SEC-010 NSC token 不刷新"
}

Q_HIGH_COST_HIGH_IMPACT: "右上 · 战略性投入 (成本高, 影响大)" {
  SEC005: "SEC-005 ACL 交集清空"
  SEC003: "SEC-003 重放窗口"
  SEC004: "SEC-004 私钥明文落盘"
  SEC006: "SEC-006 NSC 无 ACL"
  SEC015: "SEC-015 无 audit log"
}

Q_LOW_COST_LOW_IMPACT: "左下 · 排进 backlog (成本低, 影响小)" {
  SEC009: "SEC-009 token 进日志"
  SEC011: "SEC-011 device flow 不持久化"
  SEC014: "SEC-014 ACL 双写无回滚"
}

Q_HIGH_COST_LOW_IMPACT: "右下 · 高 ROI 速做 (成本高, 影响中)" {
  SEC012: "SEC-012 QUIC fingerprint"
  SEC013: "SEC-013 frame 缺 source"
}
